"  uname -sr\\fR\\[CR]\n"
"I: [sid-snap-46195b04-0893-49bf-beb8-0d4ccc899f0f chroot] Running \\e\n"
"command: \\[lq]uname -sr\\[rq]\n"
"Linux 2.6.18-3-powerpc\n"
